msgid "Help"
msgstr "Pomoć"

#: app/templates/help.html:7
msgid ""
"Grylli includes built-in instructions throughout the app to help you "
"configure and manage your setup."
msgstr ""
"Grylli uključuje ugrađena uputstva kroz aplikaciju koja pomažu pri "
"konfigurisanju i upravljanju podešavanjima."

#: app/templates/help.html:8
msgid ""
"This page provides an overview of key features and direct links to where "
"they can be managed."
msgstr ""
"Ova stranica pruža pregled ključnih funkcija i direktne linkove gde se mogu "
"upravljati."

